{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Battlewrights</strong> is a hilarious local multiplayer combat game for two to four players. The core mechanics are deceptively simple: Press button to throw your weapon, press it again to magically recall it. Repeat until you are the last person standing. Everyone can play. Every character plays the same. But if you want to take things further, try throw- and recall-jumps, charged throws, perfectly timed catch-shots and game-changing powerups. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready to fight your friends for the title of supreme Battlewright? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Everyone knows double-jumps, but have you heard of throw-jumps?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497750/extras/axe-jump.gif?t=1738679978\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Charge your throw for maximum power!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3497750/extras/charge.gif?t=1738679978\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Features</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 player couch multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try 2 of the 4 playable characters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Battle on 2 different levelsets with their own setting, powerups and interactive elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">10 different levels in total! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight for the most kills or be the last man standing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Handcrafted pixelart</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chiptune soundtrack for every stage</p></li></ul>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3497750?t=1738679978","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.stea